reviewText: I enjoyed the movies in this collection, especially Darby O'Gill and the Little People, and The Happiest Millionaire.  It was the first time I had viewed the other two films.  They were enjoyable.
Title: Disney 4-Movie Collection: Classics

reviewText: Darby O'Gill features a very young, handsome Sean Connery and some excellent special effects; Happiest Millionaire tells a true story of instustrialist Biddle features Fred MacMurray and Greer Garson; the Gnome-Mobile has great special effects, and the One and Only Genuine, Original Family Band gives a refreshing glimpse at yesteryear with its patriotism and Americana ~ a very worthwhile collection for lovers of Disney feature films.
Title: Disney 4-Movie Collection: Classics

reviewText: Walt Disney great movies.  These are wonderful family movies.  Enjoyable for all ages.  Fun to watch year after year.  They never get old.  Classic
Title: Disney 4-Movie Collection: Classics

reviewText: Just what I needed as Im laid up in bed w a upper respiratory infection. The price is great and Darby OGill is one of my favorite. I already have it on dvd and wanted The Gnomemobile but for a few more bucks I opted to buy this dvd w a few other films. I might be laid up and overly medicated but this was a great buy & I cant complain.
Title: Disney 4-Movie Collection: Classics

reviewText: This Disney movie Classic collection: Gnome Mobile, Darby O'Gill, Family Band and the Happiest Millionaire:, was received in excellent condition and very fast service. The movies are wonderfull and the speedy service of MovieMars is always excellent.  I personally believe they are one of the best sellers with Amazon.  I have never had any problem that was not taken care of by MovieMars if they supplied and shipped a movie I purchased.  This movie set was wonderful and very enjoyable.  I know I will continue to enjoy it for years to come. Thank you Amazon and MovieMars for continued great service.  Doris Seltzer
